  <brief_title>High-flow Nasal Oxygenation in Obese Patients During Apnea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Apneic Oxygenation Using High-flow Nasal Cannula in Morbidly Obese Patients Undergoing General Anesthesia</official_title>
